<item>
            <title>[LU-15912] Support autoconf 2.71</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15912</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Autoconf 2.71 causes multiple deprecation warnings and some errors when used on Lustre.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;OpenSUSE-Tumbleweed now uses 2.71 and so cannot build lustre.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;autoconf provides a program &quot;autoupdate&quot; which can be used to up update configure.am and *.m4 files.&#160; The result appears to still work with older autoconf.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
